item.description: I’m glad to announce the release of the Bilberry Hugo themeV3.8.0. This premium theme is published under an open-source license (MIT), and you can use it free of charge. It took significant amount of time to create and refine this theme. This theme is a collaborative effort of numerous volunteers.
